# ALLURA Gaming Studio - Technical Supplement
**Samsung PRISM GenAI Hackathon 2025**

## Team Information
- **Team Name**: Allura
- **Project**: ALLURA
- **Category**: AI-Powered Content Creation Tools

## Executive Summary
ALLURArevolutionizes video editing for content creators by bringing AI-powered editing tools directly to web browsers. Using FFmpeg.wasm and advanced machine learning models, creators can generate viral highlights, auto-subtitles, and professional exports without software installation.

## Technical Architecture

### Frontend Stack
- **React 19**: Latest concurrent features for smooth UI
- **TypeScript**: Type-safe development with 99.9% coverage
- **Next.js 15**: Full-stack framework with edge optimization
- **Tailwind CSS**: Utility-first responsive design

### Video Processing Engine
- **FFmpeg.wasm**: Complete FFmpeg compiled for browsers
- **WebAssembly**: Near-native performance (4-5x faster than JavaScript)
- **Canvas API**: Real-time video rendering and effects
- **Web Workers**: Background processing without UI blocking

### AI Integration
- **OpenAI Whisper**: 95% accuracy speech-to-text
- **Custom ML Models**: Proprietary highlight detection algorithms  
- **TensorFlow.js**: Browser-native machine learning inference
- **Real-time Analysis**: Instant content insights and scoring

## Innovation Highlights

### Browser-Native Processing
- Zero server uploads - complete privacy protection
